headline: Starbucks' turnaround progress after 1 year with CEO Brian Niccol
summary: It was exactly one year ago today that Brian Niccol brewed a fresh pot of coffee at Starbucks (SBUX) and took charge as the chain's new CEO. Yahoo Finance senior retail reporter Brooke DiPalma breaks down Niccol's first year as chief executive as he pushes forward on his turnaround strategy for the struggling coffee giant. Also watch Yahoo Finance's full interview with Starbucks CEO Brian Niccol from July. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
